  "title": "Childcare Indoor Cleaner (5 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Clean classrooms, toilets, common areas, offices, reception, parents’ areas, windows, doors, fans, shelves, cabinets, shoe racks, cubbies, and children’s tables and chairs (including the dining area)</li>\n  <li>Clean floor rugs, art and craft areas, and soft furnishings</li>\n  <li>Clean and sanitize areas when children soil themselves</li>\n  <li>Dispose of rubbish from classrooms and offices</li>\n  <li>Wash dishes and kitchen utensils</li>\n  <li>Maintain and track inventory of cleaning supplies</li>\n  <li>Provide assistance in the kitchen when required</li>\n  <li>Prepare simple meals as needed</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
